<div xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="習禪" xml:id="gsz0782c28shiHengTong"><lb
ed="T" n="0782c28"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0782c28"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000012462">明州雪竇院</placeName><persName key="A010617">恒通</persName>傳（<persName key="A010618">招賢岑師</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0782c29"/><persName key="A010617">釋恒通</persName>，俗姓<name>李</name>，<placeName key="PL000000001762">邢州平恩</placeName>人也。家傳士族，<pb ed="T" n="0783a" xml:id="T50.2061.0783a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0783a01"/>幼而知學。<persName key="A002599">蘇秦</persName>顯達，猶懷二頃之田<ptr target="#n1665"/>；<persName key="A003245">元亮</persName>孤<lb
ed="T" n="0783a02"/>高，不羨五<anchor xml:id="beg0783sgsz2"/>斗<anchor xml:id="end0783sgsz2"/>之祿<ptr target="#n1666"/>。縱越掞天擲地<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1618"/>，拖紫腰<lb
ed="T" n="0783a03"/>金<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1619"/>，瞬息浮華，豈裨來業？父母終禮，年甫<date key="j20300562030420" from-iso="+0846-01-01" to-iso="+0846-12-31">十<lb
ed="T" n="0783a04"/>三</date>，潛入<placeName key="PL000000020239">鵲山</placeName>訪道依師。既罷丘墳<ptr type="glossary" target="#g418"/>，唯披釋<lb
ed="T" n="0783a05"/>典，精虔懺誦，懇侍巾瓶<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1596"/>，不弭初終，蒙恩剃<lb
ed="T" n="0783a06"/>度。<date key="j20326132032977" from-iso="+0853-01-01" to-iso="+0853-12-31">年二十</date>，於本州<placeName key="PL000000001796">開元寺</placeName>具戒。後往<placeName key="PL000000042270">京兆薦<lb
ed="T" n="0783a07"/>福寺</placeName>聽習經律。七八年間，尋窮藏教，乃曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0783a08"/>「<persName key="A000883">摩騰</persName>入<placeName key="PL000000000098">漢</placeName>，譯著斯文。<ref type="person" target="#A001361">聖胄</ref>來<placeName key="PL000000000138">梁</placeName>，復明何事？」<ptr target="#n1667"/><lb
ed="T" n="0783a09"/>因辭<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">北闕</ref>，逕<anchor xml:id="beg0783sgsz4"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>請</sic><corr>詣</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0783sgsz4"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000028665">南方</ref>，遇<persName key="A010618">招賢岑<roleName>大師</roleName></persName>。<ref type="person" target="#A010618">大師</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0783a10"/>問曰：「何處人也？」曰：「<placeName key="PL000000001807">邢州</placeName>人也。」<persName key="A010618">招賢</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010618">我</ref>道<lb
ed="T" n="0783a11"/>不從彼來。」<persName key="A010617">通</persName>曰：「<ref type="person" target="#A010618">和尚</ref>還住此無？」於是有滯<lb
ed="T" n="0783a12"/>皆伸，無疑不決。後指<persName key="A009489">洞山</persName>、<persName key="A010581">石霜</persName>，皆往參焉。<lb
ed="T" n="0783a13"/><persName key="A010618">招賢</persName>示滅，<persName key="A010617">通</persName>以弟子禮事之。<date notBefore-iso="+0870-06-20" key="j20389922040636" notAfter-iso="+0874-12-20"><name>咸通</name>末</date>，遊<placeName key="PL000000016955">宣<lb
ed="T" n="0783a14"/>城</placeName>，尚書<persName key="A023013">崔<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>寓</sic><corr>璵</corr></choice></persName><ptr target="#n1668"/>素奉禪門，攀迎莊肅，覩<persName key="A010617">通</persName>儀<lb
ed="T" n="0783a15"/>表拔俗，問答往還，<persName key="A023013">崔</persName>甚悅服。於<placeName key="PL000000015305">謝仙山</placeName><ptr target="#n1673"/>奏<lb
ed="T" n="0783a16"/>置禪院，號<placeName key="PL000000057188">瑞聖</placeName>，請以居之。四方毳<anchor xml:id="beg0783sgsz5"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>衲</sic><corr>納</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0783sgsz5"/>之徒，<lb
ed="T" n="0783a17"/>不邀自聚。<persName key="A023013">博陵</persName>方議奏薦師號，堅讓遂寢。<lb
ed="T" n="0783a18"/><date notBefore-iso="+0884-05-08" key="j20440632044395" notAfter-iso="+0885-04-05"><name>中和</name>末</date>，<date notBefore-iso="+0888-04-11" key="j20454972045582" notAfter-iso="+0888-07-05"><name>文德</name>初</date>，群寇兢起<ptr target="#n1669"/>。<persName key="A010617">通</persName>領徒至<placeName key="PL000000012470">四明</placeName>。<date from-iso="+0891-02-17" key="j20465392046892" to-iso="+0892-02-05"><name>大<lb
ed="T" n="0783a19"/>順</name>二年</date>，郡牧<persName key="A007285">黃<roleName>君</roleName>晟</persName><ptr target="#n1670"/>請留居<placeName key="PL000000012462">雪竇</placeName>焉，蔚然盛<lb
ed="T" n="0783a20"/>化。<date from-iso="+0905-08-09" key="j20518252051853" to-iso="+0905-09-06"><name>天祐</name>二年七月</date>示疾，越九日躬入浴室，<lb
ed="T" n="0783a21"/>却坐繩床，集眾焚香，勤勤付囑，合掌而逝。<lb
ed="T" n="0783a22"/>春秋七十二，夏臘五十二。以<date key="j20518602051860" when-iso="+0905-09-13">其年八月七日</date><lb
ed="T" n="0783a23"/>遷石塔于<placeName key="PL000000012462">院</placeName>之西南二百餘步。或曰：「<persName key="A010617">通</persName>臨終<lb
ed="T" n="0783a24"/>言：『<ref type="person" target="#A010617">我</ref><persName key="A010620">龐勛</persName><ptr target="#n1671"/>也』。」此非也。高僧<persName key="A008812">無作</persName>為《行錄》而<lb
ed="T" n="0783a25"/>無此說。若觀年臘，<persName key="A010620">龐勛</persName>豈正弱冠來逃難<lb
ed="T" n="0783a26"/>邪？<ptr target="#n1672"/></p>
